{
  "stem": "9665.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I still had that [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Benford ?] 15-- And I was traveling a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I met his wife and the children coming back from camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But there were only three out of five.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But anyway, he wasn't by himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And his name might come with me a few minutes later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this is what I was there in that [NON-ENGLISH] all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I got a letter from my very close friend from Switzerland, Mennol Anholt and Thea, that they were in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They went out of the [NON-ENGLISH] exchange, one of the few.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they were alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I think-- I don't know when they arrived in Holland, but all this was rather emotional.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The business-- I mentioned before that Willi Eiger offered me a room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I got some quotas from-- from the distribution center where I made a living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I could have bought a house-- the most beautiful house-- with 3,000 or 4,000 cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I had millions of them, but I just felt I couldn't do that, because there was so much poverty in Holland that this didn't-- I wouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Anyway, this is-- it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We lived very, very well in a two-bedroom one in Voorburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "From Voorburg, we bought an apartment in the [NON-ENGLISH], where we had our first baby, which was Jim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] 154.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we had our first baby, which was on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we enjoyed that very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "My business was Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I went every two or three weeks to Czechoslovakia, because we didn't have a factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my brother arrived, either by the end of-- I think, in the middle of 1946.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I'm not sure about it, but around one year later after the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
